# Lab Graphicon server deployment config.
# Adjust GAZE_CSV_DIR if your participant CSV files live elsewhere on the server.
# If your server sees the storage under /mnt/hd2/29d_kon/projects instead of /hd2/projects,
# replace the prefix consistently in this file.

